Package fitnessclub

Class Member

java.lang.Object
fitnessclub.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Member>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Basic, Family, Premium
public class Member extends Object implements Comparable<Member>
Superclass meant to represent a member of fitness club. Holds the basic information of a membership the member's profile, membership expiration and chosen home studio. Should be used as a type and not as instance of an actual membership.
Author:
Ashley Berlinski
